"ESSENTIALS"

""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""

"Maps Ctrl-q To Close Current Buffer"
nnoremap <C-q> :bd<CR>

"Maps Ctrl-n To Next Buffer"
nnoremap <C-n> :bnext<CR>

"Maps Ctrl-m To Previous Buffer"
nnoremap <C-m> :bprev<CR>

"Maps Ctrl-j To Esc"
inoremap <C-j> <Esc>
vnoremap <C-j> <Esc>